label lb_w3sow_mc_wakesup:
    $ v_week = 3
    # (MC wakes up the next morning) "
    scene sc w3sowmcb b01
    with dissolve
    mc"(Mmm‚Ä¶)"
    show sc w3sowmcb b02
    mc"(Oh man, I slept pretty well last night.)"
    show sc w3sowmcb b06
    mc"(I remember feeling very tired when I went to bed, but now I feel really refreshed.)"
    show sc w3sowmcb b07
    mc"(I wonder if [s_name] is awake?)"
    show sc w3sowmcb b05
    mc"(Oh shit, I just remembered what happened up at the tower!)"
    mc"(I don‚Äôt know what possessed me to kiss [s_name] back after she kissed me.)"
    mc"(Was it because of what Ashley told her last night that caused her to do that initially?)"


label lb_w3sow_mc_wakesup_1:
    mc"(Will knowing what my father did to Ashley bring the two of us closer together, or drive us apart?)"

label lb_w3sow_mc_wakesup_2:
    mc"(Whatever happens, we have to talk it out, and just be honest with each other about how we feel.)"
    show sc w3sowmcb b07
    mc"(I‚Äôm sure what took place up at the top of the tower won‚Äôt ever happen again, will it?)"
    # (MC sits up)"
    show sc w3sowmcb b04
    mc"(Dammit... To make matters worse...)"
    mc"(I‚Äôm almost certain that I had another one of those dreams about [s_name] while I was asleep.)"
    mc"(It‚Äôs strange‚Ä¶ I seem to remember a lot about it this time. That normally doesn‚Äôt happen.)"
    show sc w3sowmcb b05
    mc"(I better go and see [s_name], because the longer I wait, the harder it will be to have a discussion with her.)"
    # (MC looks down at his stomach and thighs)"
    mc"(Actually, I should have a bath first. My whole body feels like it could do with a proper clean.)"
    mc"(Especially around my stomach area for some reason‚Ä¶)"
    # (MC looks confused or suspicious during this last line)"
    scene black
    with dissolve
    scene black
    with Pause (2)





label lb_w3sow_mc_lobby:
    scene sc w3sowkitchen k01
    with dissolve
    mc"(Hmm‚Ä¶ She‚Äôs not here. Maybe she‚Äôs still asleep.)"
    mc"(Or perhaps, she‚Äôs avoiding me‚Ä¶)"
    show sc w3sowkitchen k02
    mc"(I think it would be best if I just give her some time before I go and see her.)"
    mc"(It‚Äôs still early, so after I‚Äôve had some breakfast, hopefully by the time I‚Äôve had something she‚Äôll be awake, and then we can straighten a few things out, together.)"
    show sc w3sowkitchen k03
    mc"(It was just a kiss, it‚Äôs not like we‚Äôve never done that before. Although, we‚Äôre not kids anymore either.)"
    mc"(Sigh‚Ä¶ I just have to tell her that that can never happen again.)"
    mc"(I‚Äôm sure she‚Äôll understand.)"
    show sc w3sowkitchen k01
    mc"(Maybe once I‚Äôve prepared something to eat, I could watch the local morning news‚Ä¶)"
    mc"(Just to see if they are going to show any coverage of the wedding.)"
    # (screen goes blank)"
    scene black
    with dissolve
    scene black
    with Pause (2)
    # (scene continues in the living room, the MC has the TV on and some breakfast on the table in front of him)"
    scene sc w3sowkitchen k04
    with dissolve
    tva"And when the outgoing President was asked about the wall that wasn‚Äôt even started during his time of leadership..."
    tva"He simply told the interviewer that it was never high up on his ‚Äúto-do‚Äù list."
    show sc w3sowkitchen k07
    mc"(Of course it wasn‚Äôt‚Ä¶)"
    show sc w3sowkitchen k04
    tva"In other news, the development project that we told you about late last year has announced a new update..."
    tva"And the six thousand local investors couldn‚Äôt contain their excitement."
    show sc w3sowkitchen k05
    tva"The local business, that can‚Äôt be named for legal reasons, made announcements every quarter last year..."
    tva"But reports from the inside suggest that little to no work has been done during the past eighteen months."
    show sc w3sowkitchen k04
    tva"Some suggest that these announcements were made so that they could avoid being slapped with the dreaded ‚Äúabandoned‚Äù tag, which has been bestowed upon plenty of developers in the same industry in recent years."
    tva"Investors, however, are still willing to keep the faith."
    tva"Company owners have discarded that report as fake news and say that they're doing everything they can to deliver the full project by the next deadline."
    tva"An official date for this deadline is still yet to be announced."
    tva"Whether this project becomes officially abandoned is anybody‚Äôs guess. We‚Äôll have more details on this when they come to light."
    show sc w3sowkitchen k05
    tva"In local news now, restaurant owners are preparing for Father‚Äôs Day."
    show sc w3sowkitchen k04
    tva"It seems that most people prefer to show their love and appreciation for their Dad by taking him out..."
    tva"Rather than staying at home, going by the number of places that have confirmed numerous bookings for lunch and dinner over the past few days."
    tva"Be sure to make a booking at any of the fine restaurants we have in town otherwise you‚Äôll be making lunch or dinner for your loved one instead!"
    show sc w3sowkitchen k06
    mc"(Sigh‚Ä¶ There‚Äôs no mention about the hotel or even the wedding.)"
    mc"(Maybe it wasn‚Äôt as big of a deal as we thought it was.)"
    show sc w3sowkitchen k04
    tva"Going back to our main news bulletin, the wedding of the summer took place last night, and it‚Äôs an event that everybody is still talking about!"
    tva"The Sunshine Bay Lighthouse Hotel played host to over two hundred esteemed guests, some who travelled from various parts of the globe to witness the huge occasion."
    show sc w3sowkitchen k07
    mc"(Oh wow! They‚Äôre talking about us!)"
    show sc w3sowkitchen k08
    tva"Guests partied late into the night and some lucky attendees were able to pose for photos or selfies with pop-star Melody, who was one of the bridesmaids."
    # (IDEA: Show a pic of Vicky having a selfie with Melody on the TV screen)"
    tva"The glamour wedding has seen a huge boost for the local economy during the past week..."
    tva"And tourism experts are suggesting that the biggest winners out of all of this could be the towns‚Äô hotel owners..."
    tva"Especially the owner of the Sunshine Bay Lighthouse Hotel, who managed to put the event on with only a few days‚Äô notice."
    tva"We‚Äôll have some exclusive interviews with some of yesterday‚Äôs guests a little later in our program."
    show sc w3sowkitchen k07
    mc"(Man‚Ä¶ This is great!)"
    mc"(I should go and find [s_name] so she can see just how much exposure the hotel got because of yesterday!)"
    mc"(She‚Äôs going to be over the moon when she sees this.)"
    show sc w3sowkitchen k09
    mc"(That‚Äôs it! I have to talk to her right now!)"
    mc"(Discussing what happened between us up at the lighthouse tower can wait. This is much more important‚Ä¶)"
    scene black
    with dissolve
    scene black
    with Pause (2)




label lb_w3sow_mc_s_hotel:
