            mc"(Hmm‚Ä¶ She has quite a few missed calls and messages on here, and they‚Äôre all from Ivy and Lily!)"
            show sc w3sowkitchen k24
            mc"(They must have been trying to get in contact with [s_name] due to the success and exposure from yesterday‚Äôs wedding.)"
            show sc w3sowkitchen k25
            mc"(Damn‚Ä¶ She hasn‚Äôt replied to the twins this morning, nor has she tried to call them back.)"
            mc"(The last message she sent was last night.)"
            mc"(Sigh‚Ä¶)"
            # [Go look for [s_name] / Check her photos]"
