label lb_w3sow_connie_intro:
    scene sc w3sowboss b01
    with dissolve
    tb"When should we expect Connie home from school honey?"
    show sc w3sowboss b08
    bw"Any minute now dear."
    show sc w3sowboss b07
    bw"It feels like it‚Äôs been an eternity since we last saw her. Has it really been six months?"
    show sc w3sowboss b02
    tb"It‚Äôs been about that, yeah."
    show sc w3sowboss b03
    tb"This week is a big cause for celebration you know."
    show sc w3sowboss b08
    bw"Yes, I do dear."
    show sc w3sowboss b07
    bw"(Sigh‚Ä¶)"
    bw"I can‚Äôt believe our little girl is turning eighteen this weekend and she‚Äôs also graduating from school next week."
    show sc w3sowboss b01
    tb"Yeah, time certainly does fly."
    show sc w3sowboss b08
    bw"Oh, I better get my camera ready for when Connie walks through the front door!"
    show sc w3sowboss b05
    # (BW leaves the room)"
    tb"Have you organised the catering company for your sister‚Äôs party, Brodie?"
    show sc w3sowboss b09
    brod"Yes Dad, I just got off the phone with them."
    brod"Are you sure it was a wise idea to have Connie‚Äôs birthday party at the hotel though?"
    show sc w3sowboss b05
    tb"What do you mean son?"
    show sc w3sowboss b10
    brod"Well, I‚Äôm pretty sure she wanted an indoor pool party instead. Did she not tell you?"
    show sc w3sowboss b05
    tb"Brodie, I‚Äôm aware of what your sister wanted, but the fact of the matter is..."
    show sc w3sowboss b06
    tb"The hotel needs to regain some of the limelight back on it after the debacle of not getting that wedding that took place yesterday."
    tb"That was a huge financial miss for us son."
    show sc w3sowboss b05
    tb"And by having your sister‚Äôs eighteenth birthday party at my hotel, and more importantly in the penthouse suite..."
    show sc w3sowboss b04
    tb"It‚Äôs pretty much a guarantee that we will return to being the hotel that everyone will want to stay at in this town."
    tb"Especially with what I have planned for Saturday night‚Ä¶"
    tb"I‚Äôm sure you‚Äôve already had a look at some of the things that I have booked for her party, right?"
    show sc w3sowboss b09
    brod"Yes, I have Dad, but Connie-"
    show sc w3sowboss b27
    tb"But nothing son!"
    show sc w3sowboss b12
    tb"Trust me on this Brodie..."
    tb"I‚Äôve already let your sister‚Äôs friends and families know about the plans for this Saturday, invites have already been sent our and responded to."
    tb"Once Connie sees the work and all the stops that I‚Äôve pulled out for her birthday party..."
    tb"She‚Äôll realise that having it at the hotel was the right decision."
    show sc w3sowboss b13
    tb"It‚Äôs also a sensible decision from a business perspective."
    tb"Just make sure you don‚Äôt say anything to her about this when she arrives."
    show sc w3sowboss b14
    brod"(Sigh‚Ä¶)"
    brod"Sure, I won‚Äôt say a thing Dad."
    show sc w3sowboss b12
    tb"That‚Äôs my boy."
    # (BW returns)"
    show sc w3sowboss b11
    bw"Okay, I have the camera!"
    play sound "sound effects/01/01/Door_Knock_Sound_Effect_Free.mp3"
    show sc w3sowboss b03
    "(Knock, knock, knock)"
    tb"Good timing dear, that should be Connie now‚Ä¶"
    show sc w3sowboss b29
    bw"Oh boy, this is so exciting!"
    show sc w3sowboss b12
    tb"Get the door, will you son?"
    brod"Sure thing Dad."
    scene black
    with dissolve
    scene black
    with Pause (2)
    # (Brodie opens the door, Connie stands there, with a suitcase to her side - IMPORTANT!)"
    scene sc w3sowboss b28
    with dissolve
    bw"Welcome home honey!"
    if renpy.loadable("extras.animations") and persistent.v_anim_enabled:
        window hide
        scene wip_05_connie_intro  at tt_top
        pause
        window show
    else:
        show sc w3sowboss b16
    con"Mom!"
    # (she turns to BD)"
    scene sc w3sowboss b19
    con"Dad!!"
    con"Brodie!!"
    # (Brodie and Connie hug)"
    brod"Hey sis, it‚Äôs great to see you."
    show sc w3sowboss b15
    con"You too big brother."
    # (BW and Connie hug)"
    show sc w3sowboss b17
    bw"Oh sweetheart, it‚Äôs so great to finally have you home again."
    con"It feels great to be home Mom."
    show sc w3sowboss b20
    tb"How about a hug for your old man, huh?"
    show sc w3sowboss b18
    con"Sure Daddy."
    # (TB and Connie hug)"
    show sc w3sowboss b21
    tb"You must be hungry."
    tb"Come with me and your mother into the living room so you can tell us all about your last semester of school."
    show sc w3sowboss b22
    bw"I‚Äôll whip us up something to have for an early lunch."
    show sc w3sowboss b16
    con"Sounds great!"
    show sc w3sowboss b23
    tb"Brodie, bring Connie‚Äôs bags to her room will you?"
    show sc w3sowboss b25
    brod"Huh? Why can‚Äôt Hobson do it?"
    show sc w3sowboss b24
    tb"Because I‚Äôve already sent him home for the day."
    tb"This is a special family occasion, and it‚Äôs rare for the four of us to be together."
    tb"I even sent the gardeners home. The hired help need not be here for this."
    show sc w3sowboss b26
    brod"Ugh, fine."
