    show sc w3sowccafe c00
    c"I will, for sure."
    show sc w3sowccafe c01
    mc"The twins have also suggested that we get the staff some new work uniforms."
    show sc w3sowccafe c06
    c"Really? What will the new design look like?"
    show sc w3sowccafe c01
    mc"I have no idea."
    mc"But they already mentioned this to [s_name] last night, and they‚Äôre leaving it up to us to pick a design and order them for the staff."
    # [Ask her to model / Don‚Äôt ask]"
    menu:
        "Ask her to model"(wt="Best choice"):
            mc"I was thinking that when we get the new uniform designs, maybe you could model them for me?"
