label lb_w3sow_mc_back_hotel:
    # Week 3 (SOW) Scene 13 - SC and MC go back to the hotel"
    scene sc w3sowconarrives c01
    with dissolve
    play ambient "sound effects/01/00/water_fountain_Sound_Effect.mp3" fadein 1.0
    mc"So, this is our hotel."
    show sc w3sowconarrives c02
    c"It‚Äôs called the Sunshine Bay Lighthouse Hotel. What do you think Connie?"
    show sc w3sowconarrives c05
    con"Oh my!"
    show sc w3sowconarrives c03
    con"When you both said that you had a hotel to show me, this is nothing like the one that I had imagined in my head."
    show sc w3sowconarrives c04
    con"It looks wonderful!"
    show sc w3sowconarrives c02
    c"And this is just the entrance. Come inside so [y_name] and I can show you around."
    show sc w3sowconarrives c01
    mc"(We should probably ask Connie more about where she‚Äôs from, what her background is...)"
    mc"(And how she‚Äôs popular enough to have fifty people agree to attend her birthday party.)"
    mc"(Maybe her father is someone pretty important? I figure that he could be if he can afford a penthouse suite in town.)"
    mc"(We‚Äôll have to pick the right time to ask her about her parents and friends.)"
    stop ambient fadeout 1.0
    # (screen goes blank)"
    scene black
    with dissolve
    scene black
    with Pause (2)
    # (Connie, the MC and cousin stand in the reception area)"
    scene sc w3sowconarrives c06
    with dissolve
    c"So this is the hotel reception, which is where I‚Äôve worked a couple of times."
    con"I see."
    show sc w3sowconarrives c09
    c"It still needs some work, doesn‚Äôt it [y_name]?"
    mc"Uh, yeah, this whole area could do with an upgrade for sure."
    show sc w3sowconarrives c17
    con"No, I think it looks great."
    show sc w3sowconarrives c15
    con"But is the hotel always this quiet?"
    mc"We only just re-opened last week and pretty much all of the guests we had from the wedding yesterday have already checked out."
    show sc w3sowconarrives c12
    mc"This is what [c_name] meant when she said that we have plenty of vacant rooms at the moment."
    show sc w3sowconarrives c20
    con"And what about party planners and caterers?"
    show sc w3sowconarrives c11
    c"[y_name] and my cousin [s_name] have arguably the best party planners in Sunshine Bay, Ivy, and Lily."
    show sc w3sowconarrives c14
    c"They helped put together the wedding and the reception that was hosted here last night."
    show sc w3sowconarrives c17
    mc"And a good friend of ours, Vicky, is an incredible chef and has a lot of contacts in town."
    mc"So if you‚Äôre looking for specific dishes or if you had a birthday cake design in mind, then she would be your girl!"
    show sc w3sowconarrives c18
    con"You seem incredibly well organised considering you only re-opened the hotel last week!"
    show sc w3sowconarrives c22
    con"What about the pool area? Do you think I could see it?"
    show sc w3sowconarrives c07
    c"Of course you can. Is that okay [y_name]?"
    mc"It should be fine."
    show sc w3sowconarrives c17
    mc"The pool cleaner was here this morning and the surrounding area should be presentable again by now."
    show sc w3sowconarrives c10
    c"Great!"
    show sc w3sowconarrives c14
    c"Okay, let me show you where we would host your party if we were to have it here Connie‚Ä¶"
