    mc"(Sigh...)"
    show sc w3mowcdoor c03
    mc"(It hasn‚Äôt been this quiet around the hotel since I first arrived.)"
    mc"(It‚Äôs just not the same without [s_name] here.)"
    mc"(I know she wanted some time and probably some space...)"
    show sc w3mowcdoor c02
    mc"(But I really need to see her so I can tell her all about these plans to have Connie‚Äôs birthday party here.)"
    show sc w3mowcdoor c03
    mc"(I may have to bite the bullet and call Ashley today as she might be able to give me an idea of where [s_name] could be staying.)"
    mc"(It‚Äôs worth a shot.)"
    show sc w3mowcdoor c02
    mc"(And Connie...)"
    mc"(I wonder what [s_name] would think if I told her that she‚Äôs been staying here at the hotel, at no charge?)"
    mc"(I‚Äôm pretty sure her parents by now are really suspicious...)"
    mc"(Especially after she told her Mom that she‚Äôs been staying at a friend‚Äôs house the past couple of nights.)"
    mc"(I‚Äôm still trying to figure out the right time and place to tell her that I know who her father is.)"
    mc"(I‚Äôm surprised he hasn‚Äôt sent out a search party for his daughter yet, but he doesn‚Äôt sound like the type to panic.)"
    mc"(I haven‚Äôt seen [c_name] since she fell asleep next to me out in the pool area, and after I put her into [s_name]‚Äôs bed.)"
    show sc w3mowcdoor c01
    mc"(I don‚Äôt blame her for leaving the other morning without saying goodbye, as she was probably freaking out!)"
    mc"(I hope she didn‚Äôt get into too much trouble with her mother, Trisha.)"
    show sc w3mowcdoor c03
    mc"(I‚Äôm such an idiot for forgetting to text her to let her know that [c_name] was here.)"
    mc"(Hopefully, she‚Äôs not too mad with her daughter, or with me.)"
    show sc w3mowcdoor c01
    mc"(I‚Äôll have to call [c_name] sometime today to make sure she‚Äôs okay.)"
    mc"(And to see if she remembers anything about that kiss. I want to discuss that in person with her if possible.)"
    mc"(But first I have to talk to Connie, to find out if she knows if her original party at Seascape hotel is still going ahead or if it‚Äôs been cancelled.)"
    mc"(I‚Äôll go and see her right after I have some breakfast...)"
