label lb_w3mow_mc_connie_door:
    # Week 3 (MOW) 20 - MC decides to stick with D through her plotline"
    scene sc w3mowcdoor c04
    with dissolve
    play sound "sound effects/01/01/Door_Knock_Sound_Effect_Free.mp3"
    "(Knock, knock, knock)"
    mc"(I hope I didn't wake her up...)"
    # (ROLLING WIP of Connie)"
    if renpy.loadable("extras.animations") and persistent.v_anim_enabled:
        window hide
        scene wip_05_connie_shirt  at tt_top
        pause
        window show
    else:
        show sc w3mowcdoor c06
    con"[y_name]! Morning!"
    mc"Uh, hey Connie. How did you sleep?"
    con"Great thanks! That‚Äôs some bed you have in there."
    scene sc w3mowcdoor c09
    con"You‚Äôre really lucky, I could‚Äôve slept all day in it!"
    show sc w3mowcdoor c06
    mc"Uh, yeah."
    show sc w3mowcdoor c07
    mc"Anyway, Connie, I was just wondering if you‚Äôve heard from your parents?"
    mc"Surely by now they would‚Äôve clued on to the fact you‚Äôre not staying at your friend‚Äôs place as you said, and-"
    show sc w3mowcdoor c11
    con"Look, I‚Äôm sorry if I‚Äôm putting you out [y_name]."
    show sc w3mowcdoor c08
    con"What if I paid to stay in one of the hotel rooms from now on? Would that solve the problem? I can also give you money for the nights I've already stayed here as well."
    show sc w3mowcdoor c07
    mc"Yeah, but what about your parents? It doesn‚Äôt really solve that particular issue."
    show sc w3mowcdoor c12
    con"You let me take care of them. Don‚Äôt worry about it [y_name], I can handle it."
    show sc w3mowcdoor c06
    con"By the way, I‚Äôve told some of my closest friends that a pool party is still going ahead for my birthday..."
    con"And that I‚Äôll message them with the exact details on Friday night."
    con"That way, it keeps the location, which is here, a secret until the night before..."
    con"But it also gives you time to discuss the plans for it with [s_name]."
    show sc w3mowcdoor c12
    con"When you see her that is."
    show sc w3mowcdoor c06
    mc"(Hmm...)"
    mc"(That‚Äôs kind of cutting it close, but if her father doesn‚Äôt know the location until late Friday or even early Saturday...)"
    mc"(Then he won‚Äôt be able to do anything about it if all of Connie‚Äôs friends show up here instead of his hotel.)"
    mc"(But for the time being, Connie will have to lay low, so her parents can‚Äôt talk her out of it.)"
    show sc w3mowcdoor c07
    mc"All right, that sounds okay I guess."
    mc"Maybe it‚Äôs best you don‚Äôt speak to your parents or anyone else for the time being."
    mc"And as far as your Dad is concerned, he probably thinks your party is going to be at his hotel, correct?"
    show sc w3mowcdoor c12
    con"He does, yeah."
    show sc w3mowcdoor c09
    con"Oh man, I‚Äôd love to see the look on his face when he realises that my party has been moved here!"
    show sc w3mowcdoor c06
    mc"(Connie might see the funny side of it, but her Dad doesn‚Äôt seem like the kind of guy to piss off.)"
    mc"(And I‚Äôm sure we've already infuriated him by hosting that wedding here last Saturday.)"
    mc"(I wonder if he‚Äôs sent any of his people out into town to look for Connie?)"
    mc"(Like the police for instance?)"
    show sc w3mowcdoor c07
    con"So, have you heard anything from [s_name] this morning?"
    mc"Unfortunately, no, I haven't. But there‚Äôs one person I know who might have an idea as to where she might be."
    mc"But for now, please don‚Äôt go anywhere. At least not until I get back, okay?"
    show sc w3mowcdoor c06
    con"Sure, I can do that."
    show sc w3mowcdoor c10
    con"Where are you going anyway?"
    show sc w3mowcdoor c07
    mc"I have to head out and run some errands, but I shouldn‚Äôt be too long."
    con"Would it be okay if I get myself some breakfast in the kitchen?"
    mc"Haha yes, of course you can."
    # (Connie kisses the MC on the cheek)"
    play sound "sound effects/01/01/short_kiss_sound_effect.mp3"
    show sc w3mowcdoor c13
    con"Mwah!"
    show sc w3mowcdoor c09
    con"If I didn‚Äôt say it before [y_name], I really appreciate you letting me stay here."
    show sc w3mowcdoor c06
    con"I definitely owe you one."
    # (Connie holds his wrist and looks up at the MC)"
    mc"Um‚Ä¶ It‚Äôs no trouble at all."
    mc"(Is it just my imagination, or was there more to that kiss than I think there was?)"
    # (Connie turns so we see her from behind, head over her shoulder)"
    show sc w3mowcdoor c12
    con"So I‚Äôm gonna go take a shower. I‚Äôll see you when you get back [y_name]."
    show sc w3mowcdoor c06
    mc"Sure... Bye Connie."
    # (Connie closes her door)"
    show sc w3mowcdoor c05
    mc"(Sigh‚Ä¶ All right, I better get a move on, as I have plenty of things that I need to do today‚Ä¶)"
    scene black
