label lb_w3mow_mc_calls_ashley:
    # Week 3 (MOW) 24 - The MC calls Ashley"
    scene sc w3sowkitchen k01
    with dissolve
    mc"(Sigh‚Ä¶ Well, this could be my final hope of finding [s_name].)"
    mc"(Here goes nothing‚Ä¶)"
    # [Call Ashley]"
    # (Phone dialling sound effect)"
    play sound "sound effects/01/00/Phone_call_dialling_sound_effect.mp3" loop
    "..."
    # (*for the Ashley phone call shots, have her sitting in her car while on the phone)"
    stop sound
    ash"Hello?"
    mc"Ashley, hey, it‚Äôs [y_name]."
    ash"Oh, hey [y_name]. I was wondering when I was going to hear from you again."
    ash"How are things?"
    mc"Yeah, they‚Äôre okay, except‚Ä¶"
    ash"Except for what? Is everything all right?"
    mc"(Sigh‚Ä¶)"
    mc"You haven‚Äôt seen or heard from [s_name] by any chance, have you?"
    ash"No, I haven‚Äôt. Why, is she not there at the hotel with you right now?"
    mc"No, she isn‚Äôt."
    jump lb_w3mow_mc_calls_ashley_1

label lb_w3mow_mc_calls_ashley_1:
    ash"I‚Äôm sure she‚Äôs fine. She‚Äôs probably just being a drama queen after what I told her about your father the other night."
    jump lb_w3mow_mc_calls_ashley_2

label lb_w3mow_mc_calls_ashley_2:
    ash"How many hours has it been since you last spoke to her?"
    mc"Hours? I haven‚Äôt seen her in three days!"
    ash"Three days?!?! Well, why didn‚Äôt you call me sooner??"
    mc"I‚Äôm sorry, I wanted to, but I held off because [s_name] did in fact message me the other night to let me know that she was safe..."
    mc"And that she needed some time to herself. She wouldn‚Äôt tell me where she was though."
    mc"I‚Äôm just concerned because it‚Äôs been a few days now..."
    mc"I‚Äôm running this hotel pretty much all by myself, and we have a prospective client who wants to have an event here this weekend."
    mc"So I could really do with her being here."
    ash"Hmm, it certainly does sound like she needs to be there for you."
