label lb_w3mow_mc_con_beach_house:
    # Week 3 (MOW) 26 - MC picks SC up and they go to the beach house with Connie"
    scene sc w3mowconniesc c01
    with dissolve
    mc"(Home, safe and sound‚Ä¶)"
    mc"Connie? [c_name]?"
    c"Hey [y_name]."
    show sc w3mowconniesc c03
    mc"What are you doing here?"
    show sc w3mowconniesc c01
    c"I came to see how you both were doing. And to bring Connie some clean clothes."
    show sc w3mowconniesc c03
    c"Where have you been?"
    mc"I went to see  your aunt Ashley."
    mc"She suggested that we check out her beach house, as she thinks that [s_name] could have been staying there the past few days."
    show sc w3mowconniesc c07
    mc"Connie, did you tell [c_name] what happened this morning?"
    show sc w3mowconniesc c06
    con"Yeah, I filled her in."
    show sc w3mowconniesc c04
    c"Connie also told me that you might have a plan in mind for where she could be moved to."
    show sc w3mowconniesc c03
    mc"Yes, I do!"
    mc"So as I said, Ashley said that we should check out her beach house..."
    show sc w3mowconniesc c07
    mc"But she also said that Connie can stay there for the next few nights if she wants to."
    con"She‚Äôs okay with that?"
    mc"Yeah, actually she insisted. And Ashley has provided me with a key to her place as well."
    show sc w3mowconniesc c05
    con"I don‚Äôt know what to say. Thanks so much you guys!"
    mc"It was nothing."
    show sc w3mowconniesc c07
    mc"But I suggest that we move you there right now, just in case someone from your father‚Äôs hotel comes back to look for you again."
    show sc w3mowconniesc c05
    con"Yes, I agree."
    show sc w3mowconniesc c07
    con"Um, give me a few minutes to pack some of the things that I have in your room."
    # (Connie leaves)"
    show sc w3mowconniesc c11
    # (MC turns to cousin)"
    mc"So, uh, how did you pull up after the other night?"
    show sc w3mowconniesc c13
    c"Yeah, I was pretty tired as you know. I think I may have had a bit too much to drink."
    show sc w3mowconniesc c12
    mc"I‚Äôm sorry if I got you into trouble with your Mom."
    show sc w3mowconniesc c11
    mc"I wanted to text Trisha to let her know that you were here, but I forgot to. She must have been worried sick about you."
    show sc w3mowconniesc c10
    c"Honestly, it‚Äôs okay [y_name]."
    mc"Huh? How do you mean?"
    c"Well, I left here at about six o‚Äôclock in the morning, and then I went straight home."
    show sc w3mowconniesc c11
    c"When I walked through the front door, I was expecting my Mom to be there waiting for me."
    show sc w3mowconniesc c12
    c"But as it turned out, she was out all night and she never returned home either!"
    c"She had no idea that I fell asleep here!"
    show sc w3mowconniesc c11
    mc"Oh wow! Really?"
    show sc w3mowconniesc c10
    c"Yeah, I couldn‚Äôt believe it."
    show sc w3mowconniesc c11
    c"In the end, she ended up apologising to me for not coming home and not telling me."
    mc"Haha! That‚Äôs pretty funny, not to mention incredibly fortunate."
    show sc w3mowconniesc c13
    c"[y_name], thanks for looking after me and for giving up [s_name]‚Äôs bed for me to sleep in."
    show sc w3mowconniesc c11
    mc"You‚Äôre welcome. As the guy currently in charge of running this hotel, I have to look after all our guests!"
    show sc w3mowconniesc c10
    c"Oh, so I was a guest the other night? I thought I was a co-owner of this place?"
    mc"Haha, you are, but on my watch, you‚Äôre also a very special guest."
    mc"(Damn, this would be the perfect time to talk to [c_name] about that kiss the other night.)"
    # (Cousin smiles)"
    # (Connie returns)"
    show sc w3mowconniesc c08
    con"Okay, I‚Äôm ready to go."
    mc"(Damn, well there goes that idea! That discussion will have to wait...)"
    show sc w3mowconniesc c12
    c"So how are we going to get there [y_name]? There are three of us, so we can‚Äôt all fit on a scooter."
    show sc w3mowconniesc c08
    mc"Hmm‚Ä¶ We‚Äôre gonna need a car."
    show sc w3mowconniesc c09
    con"I could order us an Uber if you‚Äôd like?"
    mc"That would be best."
    con"And I‚Äôd like to pay for it too. I mean, you guys have looked after me so well, so I‚Äôm more than happy to cover the cost."
    con"And on top of that, I really want to have my birthday party at your hotel, no matter what."
    con"I can transfer you a deposit today to make that happen."
    mc"That‚Äôs great to hear Connie!"
    show sc w3mowconniesc c14
    c"You won‚Äôt be disappointed!"
    show sc w3mowconniesc c15
    show screen scr_rewards("sc w3mowconniesc c15b","v_rewards_connie_4")
    con"I‚Äôm sure I won‚Äôt."
    hide screen scr_rewards
    show sc w3mowconniesc c09
    con"Give me a moment to order this Uber."
    # (Connie orders the Uber through her phone app)"
    mc"Once you‚Äôve done that, then we‚Äôll wait out the front of the hotel for it to arrive."
    show sc w3mowconniesc c10
    mc"In the meantime, I‚Äôll call the twins to see if they can stop by to watch the hotel for a few hours this afternoon‚Ä¶"
    scene black
    with dissolve
    scene black
    with Pause (2)
    scene sc w3mowconniesc c16
    with dissolve
    play ambient "sound effects/01/03/Car Driving Interior Sound FX.mp3" fadein 1.0
    c"This is a nice car, and the air-conditioning is a godsend on such a hot day!"
    con"Yeah, it‚Äôs the best way to travel."
    # (Connie addresses the Uber driver)"
    show sc w3mowconniesc c17
    con"We‚Äôre ready to go now, driver."
    # (the Uber takes off)"
    show sc w3mowconniesc c18
    mc"(Sigh‚Ä¶ Okay, I can kind of relax, now that Connie is out of the hotel.)"
    mc"(None of her father‚Äôs people will ever know that she was here.)"
    show sc w3mowconniesc c20
    mc"(I just hope [s_name] is at her Mom‚Äôs beach house when we get there.)"
    show sc w3mowconniesc c19
    mc"(I‚Äôll find out soon enough.)"
    stop ambient fadeout 1.0
    # (outside, Lucas from behind some bushes watches as the Uber drives away)"
    play ambient "sound effects/01/01/Birds_in_trees_sounds_effects1.mp3" fadein 1.0
    show sc w3mowconniesc c23
    lu"(A-ha! I knew there was something that guy was keeping from me!)"
    show sc w3mowconniesc c22
    lu"(So that cocky little bitch has been hiding here in this hotel.)"
    show sc w3mowconniesc c23
    lu"(Oh, the boss is gonna love me for this.)"
    show sc w3mowconniesc c22
    lu"(Hmm, I won‚Äôt be able to follow them, as my stupid scooter won‚Äôt be able to keep up.)"
    show sc w3mowconniesc c23
    lu"(But they‚Äôll probably be back sometime later today, so I‚Äôll call the boss and let him know.)"
    lu"(That ten grand is as good as mine! Hahaha!!)"
    stop ambient fadeout 1.0
    scene black
    with dissolve
    scene black
    with Pause (2)






