    show sc w3mowbhouse b33
    s"All right, you have a lot of explaining to do [y_name]."
    s"So who is this girl and why on earth is she going to be staying here?"
    show sc w3mowbhouse b32
    mc"Okay, but before I tell you the whole story, you need to know that your Mom is okay with Connie holing up here for a few days."
    mc"Anyway, as I said, a lot has happened in the past few days while you‚Äôve been gone."
    show sc w3mowbhouse b36
    mc"Let me start from the beginning, when [c_name] and I met Connie in a coffee shop in town‚Ä¶"
    scene black
    with dissolve
    scene black
    with Pause (2)
    # (scene continues after MC has explained the whole story to S)"
    scene sc w3mowbhouse b33
    with dissolve
    mc"...So after she told us about her argument with her father, Connie asked if she could stay at the hotel, as she had nowhere else to go."
    show sc w3mowbhouse b36
    s"Okay, I kind of get it."
    show sc w3mowbhouse b32
    s"But you still haven‚Äôt explained to me why this girl needs to stay here in my Mom‚Äôs beach house."
    show sc w3mowbhouse b33
    mc"This morning when I returned to the hotel after speaking with your Mom, there was some guy poking around."
    mc"I knew he wasn‚Äôt one of our guests so I confronted him."
    mc"After he left, Connie told me that she‚Äôd seen him before and that her father probably sent this guy out to try and find her."
    mc"I also believe it‚Äôs the same guy who attacked you after you left Victoria‚Äôs place a couple of weeks ago."
    show sc w3mowbhouse b38
    s"Oh my God! Seriously?? What did you tell him?"
    show sc w3mowbhouse b32
    mc"I didn‚Äôt get a chance to respond, as he had to answer a phone call. He then left shortly after."
    s"How do know for sure that it was the same guy who attacked me?"
    mc"He pretty much gave himself away. He asked for you specifically and he was able to describe you."
    mc"And uh‚Ä¶"
    mc"(I have to tell her the truth about Connie. [s_name] is going to find out one way or another.)"
    show sc w3mowbhouse b37
    s"What is it [y_name]?"
    show sc w3mowbhouse b32
    mc"This guy also works for the man who owns Seascape hotel‚Ä¶ Brodie‚Äôs father."
    show sc w3mowbhouse b38
    s"Oh..."
    s"Wait! That would mean that this guy‚Äôs boss is‚Ä¶"
    mc"Yeah, he‚Äôs Connie‚Äôs father. And Brodie is her brother."
    # (screen shakes)"
    s"Oh my god?!? Why on earth would you bring her here [y_name]??"
    show sc w3mowbhouse b32
    s"Is she trying to get me to sell my hotel to her Dad as well?"
    mc"No, no‚Ä¶ You don‚Äôt understand [s_name]. Connie isn‚Äôt like her Dad or Brodie."
    mc"As I said, she had a huge fight with her father about where she wanted her birthday party to be held this Saturday..."
    show sc w3mowbhouse b33
    mc"Which is the reason why she was so upset when [c_name] and I first met her in the coffee shop."
    mc"We showed Connie the hotel pool area and she just told us that she wants her eighteenth birthday party to be at your hotel."
    # (S not convinced)"
    show sc w3mowbhouse b39
    s"That‚Äôs ridiculous [y_name]! There‚Äôs no way possible that this girl is legit. I don‚Äôt trust her."
    show sc w3mowbhouse b32
    mc"Oh really?"
    mc"Well, what if I told you that she‚Äôs already transferred a two grand deposit into the hotel account..."
    mc"Just to ensure that her party will take place this Saturday?"
    show sc w3mowbhouse b36
    s"She has?"
    show sc w3mowbhouse b33
    mc"Yeah, it‚Äôs already in there."
    mc"And Connie has messaged some of her friends to tell them that her party won‚Äôt be at her father‚Äôs hotel as originally planned."
    mc"She‚Äôs going to send out a text with the full details on Friday night."
    mc"We just have to make sure that her father or any of his people don‚Äôt find her before Saturday, hence why she has to stay here."
    mc"The hotel just wasn‚Äôt a safe place for her anymore."
    show sc w3mowbhouse b37
    s"Hmm‚Ä¶ I still don‚Äôt know about this [y_name]. Have you told Ivy or Lily about Connie or this party she wants to have?"
    mc"They know everything [s_name]."
    show sc w3mowbhouse b32
    mc"They know about the party, and who Connie‚Äôs father is."
    mc"And they‚Äôre all for the idea to have the party at your hotel."
    mc"They‚Äôve already started putting plans in place for it."
    show sc w3mowbhouse b33
    s"Does Connie have any idea that you know who her Dad is? Or Brodie?"
    mc"No, she has no idea. And I want to keep it that way."
    mc"She‚Äôll eventually find out, but it‚Äôs best that she doesn‚Äôt know for now."
    show sc w3mowbhouse b37
    s"(Sigh‚Ä¶)"
    s"Look, I‚Äôm still against this idea, but you, [c_name], and the twins seem to be all for it."
    s"I‚Äôm not sure what to do here [y_name]."
    show sc w3mowbhouse b32
    mc"Just come and talk to Connie. You‚Äôll see that she‚Äôs nothing like her Dad or brother."
    mc"And you don‚Äôt need to tell her how you know Brodie. Besides, it seems like she doesn‚Äôt have a clue that you two were dating."
    mc"I mean, when you met her, Connie didn‚Äôt react like she knew who you were, right?"
    s"No, no she didn‚Äôt."
    mc"Please just trust me on this one, [s_name]."
    show sc w3mowbhouse b39
    s"Okay, fine. Let‚Äôs go and see her and [c_name]‚Ä¶"
    scene black
    with dissolve
    scene black
    with Pause (2)



label lb_w3mow_night_beach_house:
    #     Week 3 (MOW) 28 - They decide to spend the afternoon and night at the Beach house"
    scene sc w3mowbhouse b47
    with dissolve
    play ambient "sound effects/01/00/soft_ocean_waves.mp3" fadein 1.0
    c"(Hmm‚Ä¶ [y_name] and [s_name] have been in there for quite a long while.)"
    c"(Are they arguing?)"
    show sc w3mowbhouse b44
    c"(They‚Äôve had so much tension between them, is it simply due to the hotel, or is something else going on between them?)"
    show sc w3mowbhouse b45
    c"(Oh! Why am I obsessing over this so much?)"
    show sc w3mowbhouse b46
    c"(Is it because I‚Äôve spent so much time with [y_name] when we were looking for [s_name] the other day?)"
    show sc w3mowbhouse b45
    c"(It‚Äôs almost like I‚Äôm feeling a little‚Ä¶ Jealous.)"
    show sc w3mowbhouse b53
    c"(Wait! Am I jealous of my cousin [s_name]? No, that‚Äôs ridiculous‚Ä¶)"
    show sc w3mowbhouse b46
    c"(I can't stop thinking about that kiss we shared as well. What if he doesn't want to talk about it?)"
    c"(There's no way I'd bring it up with [y_name], I'd be too scared to.)"
    show sc w3mowbhouse b40
    con"This house is incredible!"
    show sc w3mowbhouse b41
    con"I wonder how much your aunt paid for this place?"
    show sc w3mowbhouse b48
    c"Uh, I‚Äôm not sure, but I think it would be worth quite a lot now."
    show sc w3mowbhouse b41
    con"Do you know how long she‚Äôs had it for?"
    show sc w3mowbhouse b49
    s"About five years now."
    s"She‚Äôs had renovations done to each room every so often over that time."
    s"One of the bathrooms is currently being worked on at the moment though."
    show sc w3mowbhouse b42
    con"I see."
    show sc w3mowbhouse b50
    s"Connie‚Ä¶ Do you mind if we had a word inside?"
    show sc w3mowbhouse b43
    con"Oh‚Ä¶ I guess that would be okay."
    show sc w3mowbhouse b52
    mc"[s_name], do you want me to-"
    show sc w3mowbhouse b51
    s"It‚Äôs okay [y_name], we‚Äôll be fine."
    show sc w3mowbhouse b54
    s"Maybe you and [c_name] could stay here and enjoy the view."
    mc"Oh, all right‚Ä¶"
    stop ambient fadeout 1.0
    scene black
    with dissolve
    scene black
    with Pause (2)
    scene sc w3mowbhouse b55
    with dissolve
    menu:
        "Connie and [s_name]":
            $ v_w3mow_night_beach_house_connie = True
            scene black
            with dissolve
            scene black
            with Pause (2)
            jump lb_w3mow_night_beach_house_connie

        "[y_name] and [c_name]":
            $ v_w3mow_night_beach_house_mc = True
            scene black
            with dissolve
            scene black
            with Pause (2)
            jump lb_w3mow_night_beach_house_mc



label lb_w3mow_night_beach_house_connie:
    scene sc w3mowbhouse b61
    with dissolve
    con"So, what did you want to talk about?"
    show sc w3mowbhouse b58
    s"First off I just wanted to give my apologies if I‚Äôve made you feel uncomfortable since you got here."
    s"I‚Äôve been having a lot of trust issues of late, and I sometimes don‚Äôt warm to people immediately."
    show sc w3mowbhouse b60
    con"I understand."
    show sc w3mowbhouse b62
    con"I‚Äôve been having a lot of trust issues with people really close to me as well."
    con"I know it‚Äôs not the same thing..."
    con"But I get why you would be hesitant to trust someone you don‚Äôt even know or that you‚Äôve only just met."
    show sc w3mowbhouse b57
    s"Look Connie, I want to trust you, I really do."
    show sc w3mowbhouse b58
    s"My hotel is very important to me..."
    s"And if I make any decisions regarding any events or guests staying there, then I have to be one hundred percent sure I‚Äôm correct when I do so."
    jump lb_w3mow_night_beach_house_connie_1


label lb_w3mow_night_beach_house_connie_1:
    s"And then there‚Äôs [y_name]."
    s"He‚Äôs putting a lot of faith in you being able to come through for us, despite only knowing you for less than a week."



label lb_w3mow_night_beach_house_connie_2:
    s"I‚Äôve had issues with your father and his hotel in recent months, so as you can see, I‚Äôm feeling very reluctant to agree to host your party."
    show sc w3mowbhouse b62
    con"I understand your concerns [s_name]. And I know it doesn‚Äôt look good..."
    show sc w3mowbhouse b61
    con"But as [y_name] said, I‚Äôve already put down a decent deposit just to show how serious I am, and as a sign of good faith."
    show sc w3mowbhouse b62
    con"My father doesn‚Äôt care about what I want, he only cares about himself and his hotel."
    con"And after spending time with [y_name] and your cousin [c_name]..."
    show sc w3mowbhouse b60
    con"I know for sure that they only want what‚Äôs best for me, and they care about what I actually want for my party."
    show sc w3mowbhouse b57
    s"(Hmm‚Ä¶ She sounds genuine, but I need to push her further.)"
    s"(She has absolutely no idea that I‚Äôve dated her brother, so I could use that to find out some more truth, or maybe even lies.)"
    s"Can I ask you a personal question?"
    show sc w3mowbhouse b60
    con"Yes, for sure."
    show sc w3mowbhouse b58
    s"What‚Äôs the rest of your family like? Do you have a big family?"
    show sc w3mowbhouse b61
    con"Oh, well, there‚Äôs just the four of us."
    con"My Mom is really sweet, but she sometimes agrees too much with my father and takes his side instead of mine."
    con"I have an older brother as well. His name is Brodie."
    show sc w3mowbhouse b58
    s"Oh, and what‚Äôs he like?"
    show sc w3mowbhouse b61
    con"Well I haven‚Äôt seen him much in the past few years because I‚Äôve been going to an all-girls boarding school outside of town you see."
    show sc w3mowbhouse b60
    con"But we used to be close when we were growing up."
    show sc w3mowbhouse b57
    s"And you‚Äôre not now?"
    show sc w3mowbhouse b62
    con"Not really."
    con"I mean, his heart is usually in the right place, but he‚Äôs become more like our father which I know is not a good thing."
    con"He‚Äôs likely going to take over our father‚Äôs business when he retires and I worry that he might become exactly like him."
    show sc w3mowbhouse b58
    s"Yeah, I can imagine."
    show sc w3mowbhouse b62
    con"A part of me hopes that he won‚Äôt, but he wouldn‚Äôt listen to me even when I‚Äôve tried to talk to him about it."
    con"He says I wouldn‚Äôt understand because I‚Äôm a girl."
    show sc w3mowbhouse b57
    s"(That doesn‚Äôt sound like Brodie at all.)"
    s"(Maybe‚Äôs he‚Äôs changed, and he's become really influenced by his Dad.)"
    s"You don‚Äôt want anything to do with your father‚Äôs business at all?"
    show sc w3mowbhouse b62
    con"No‚Ä¶ I‚Äôm nothing like my father or my brother."
    con"It‚Äôs not what I want for my future, and my father simply doesn‚Äôt understand."
    con"Look, you have no reason to trust me [s_name], but I want you to know that I owe [y_name] and [c_name] a lot."
    show sc w3mowbhouse b60
    con"And if having my party at your hotel can you help you guys out..."
    con"And if it also makes a point to my father at the same time, then I would really like this to happen."
    show sc w3mowbhouse b63
    con"More than anything in the world."
    show sc w3mowbhouse b57
    s"(Oh boy‚Ä¶ She really does resent her father.)"
    s"(And if [y_name]‚Äôs suspicions are correct, then Connie also wants to have her party at my hotel to spite or maybe even embarrass him.)"
    s"(Hmm...)"
    s"(I can only imagine what the ramifications will be if or when her Dad finds out that her party is at our hotel and not at his.)"
    show sc w3mowbhouse b56
    s"Okay, I‚Äôve made a decision. We‚Äôre going to have your party at my hotel."
    show sc w3mowbhouse b63
    con"Oh my God! We are?"
    show sc w3mowbhouse b56
    s"Yes. Now that I‚Äôve heard your side of the story Connie I‚Äôm willing to take a chance."
    s"I have a pretty good feeling about this."
    show sc w3mowbhouse b63
    con"Thank you so much [s_name]! I promise you won‚Äôt regret it!"
    show sc w3mowbhouse b56
    s"Haha! Come on."
    show sc w3mowbhouse b59
    s"Let‚Äôs go and see what [y_name] and [c_name] are doing."
    scene black
    with dissolve
    scene black
    with Pause (2)
    if v_w3mow_night_beach_house_mc:
        jump lb_w3mow_night_beach_house_ending

    $ v_w3mow_night_beach_house_mc = True
    jump lb_w3mow_night_beach_house_mc









label lb_w3mow_night_beach_house_mc:

    scene sc w3mowbhouse b65
    with dissolve
    play ambient "sound effects/01/00/soft_ocean_waves.mp3" fadein 1.0
    c"Is everything okay between you and [s_name]?"
    mc"I believe so."
    show sc w3mowbhouse b64
    mc"She‚Äôs still unsure about Connie and her intentions for this party."
    show sc w3mowbhouse b69
    c"But why? She seems really sweet."
    show sc w3mowbhouse b64
    mc"I know, but we‚Äôll know more after they‚Äôve had a chat."
    show sc w3mowbhouse b70
    c"So, what do you think [s_name] is talking to Connie about?"
    show sc w3mowbhouse b64
    mc"I don‚Äôt know, but if I were to take a guess, I‚Äôd say she‚Äôs checking to see how genuine Connie is about having her party at the hotel."
    show sc w3mowbhouse b66
    c"I hope [s_name] lets her do it."
    show sc w3mowbhouse b70
    c"I really like Connie a lot. What do you think of her?"
    # [I like her / She‚Äôs okay]"
    show sc w3mowbhouse b64
    menu:
        "I like her"(wt="Best choice"):
            mc"Yeah, I like her too. And I can tell that you two have been getting on rather well."
            show sc w3mowbhouse b67
            c"Oh yeah, she‚Äôs really easy to talk to, and I have you to thank for that."
            show sc w3mowbhouse b66
            mc"Me? What did I do?"
            c"I don‚Äôt know..."
            show sc w3mowbhouse b68
            c"I think spending time together has helped me to be comfortable around new people, especially girls my own age."
            show sc w3mowbhouse b64
            mc"Haha, you could be right."
            mc"However, it was you that got up to talk to her in the coffee shop, and there was no prompting from me."
            mc"You did it yourself [c_name]."
            show sc w3mowbhouse b67
            $ c_points = change_stat(c_points,2,c_name)
            c"Yeah, I really did!"
            show sc w3mowbhouse b66
        "She‚Äôs okay":
            show sc w3mowbhouse b64
            mc"She‚Äôs okay I guess. Connie does seem quite sure of herself and she knows what she wants."
            mc"I like that in a girl."
            show sc w3mowbhouse b68
            c"Oh‚Ä¶"
            # (Cousin dismayed to hear the MC talk up Connie in front of her)"
            show sc w3mowbhouse b65
            $ c_points = change_stat(c_points,-2,c_name)
            mc"(Hmm‚Ä¶ Did I say something wrong?)"
            # (scene continues)"

    # [Ask for her help / Don‚Äôt ask]"
    menu:
        "Ask for her help"(wt="Best choice"):
            show sc w3mowbhouse b64
            mc"So, if [s_name] signs off on having Connie‚Äôs party..."
            mc"You know we‚Äôre going to need someone to help sign our guests in at the hotel."
            mc"Are you free on Saturday?"
            show sc w3mowbhouse b67
            c"Yes, I am!"
            show sc w3mowbhouse b71
            c"I was going to ask if you wanted me to help you and [s_name] again."
            show sc w3mowbhouse b66
            mc"Of course, we need you [c_name]!"
            $ c_points = change_stat(c_points,2,c_name)
            mc"You‚Äôre part of our team now and the wedding may not have been the same without you."
            show sc w3mowbhouse b67
            c"Thanks [y_name]! That means a lot to me."
            show sc w3mowbhouse b66
            mc"(Hmm‚Ä¶ I really want to ask [c_name] about the other night by the pool, because I‚Äôm sure she‚Äôs still thinking about it too.)"
            mc"(But maybe now isn‚Äôt the right time...)"
            mc"(Especially with all the drama of finding [s_name] and then introducing her to Connie.)"
            # (Cousin smiles)"
        "Don‚Äôt ask":
            show sc w3mowbhouse b70
            c"I‚Äôve been meaning to ask you [y_name]..."
            show sc w3mowbhouse b71
            c"If [s_name] signs off on having Connie‚Äôs party, will you and [s_name] need some help on Saturday?"
            show sc w3mowbhouse b64
            mc"Yeah, we certainly will."
            mc"We‚Äôre definitely going to need someone to help sign our guests in at the hotel."
            mc"Are you free on Saturday?"
            show sc w3mowbhouse b67
            c"Yes, I am!"
            show sc w3mowbhouse b66
            mc"I‚Äôm glad you asked because I may not have thought to ask you."
            mc"You‚Äôre part of our team now [c_name], and the wedding may not have been the same without you."
            show sc w3mowbhouse b67
            c"Thanks [y_name]! That means a lot to me."
            show sc w3mowbhouse b66
            mc"(Hmm‚Ä¶ I really want to ask [c_name] about the other night by the pool, because I‚Äôm sure she‚Äôs still thinking about it too.)"
            mc"(But maybe now isn‚Äôt the right time...)"
            mc"(Especially with all the drama of finding [s_name] and then introducing her to Connie.)"
    # (screen goes blank)"
    # [Head back / Ask her plans]"
    menu:
        "Head back"(wt="This will END the [c_name] path"):
            show sc w3mowbhouse b64
            mc"So uh, maybe we could head back to the house now."
            mc"I think that should be enough time."
            show sc w3mowbhouse b65
            c"Uh, yeah, it should be."
            show sc w3mowbhouse b64
            mc"Hopefully all is well and by the time we‚Äôve spoken with [s_name], we‚Äôll have a party to start preparing for."
            show sc w3mowbhouse b66
            c"Yeah, let‚Äôs hope so!"
            if v_w2eow_c_shopping:
                #‚ÄúAdd these lines if the player got all three questions right in ‚ÄúWeek 2 (EOW) Scene 16.5 - The MC visits Cousin in reception‚Äù
                show sc w3mowbhouse b70
                c"(Hmm‚Ä¶ [y_name] hasn‚Äôt said anything about us doing something together...)"
                c"(After I told him about the surf store I was looking to visit at the mall.)"
                show sc w3mowbhouse b69
                c"(Maybe he‚Äôs forgotten that I mentioned it to him?)"
                c"(Sigh‚Ä¶ I‚Äôm too scared to ask him again, and I don‚Äôt want to sound like I‚Äôm needy.)"
                c"(Maybe it‚Äôs best if I don‚Äôt say anything about it‚Ä¶)"
            stop ambient fadeout 1.0

        "Ask [c_name] her plans"(wt="You will be on the [c_name] path"):
            #*Choosing this option will set up a lunch date with Cousin in v6"
            $ v_w3mow_c_date = True
            show sc w3mowbhouse b64
            mc"So I was wondering, do you have any plans on Sunday afternoon [c_name]?"
            show sc w3mowbhouse b71
            c"This Sunday? Oh, I don‚Äôt think so. I might do something with [s_name] in the morning, seeing as it's Father's Day..."
            c"But I‚Äôm normally free on Sunday afternoons. How come?"
            show sc w3mowbhouse b64
            mc"Well, I was thinking that maybe we could hang out and do something fun together?"
            show sc w3mowbhouse b69
            c"(Oh my! Is he asking me out on a date??)"
            show sc w3mowbhouse b64
            mc"That is if you‚Äôre up for hanging out with this guy!"
            # (MC points to himself with a finger on each hand)"
            mc"As friends of course."
            show sc w3mowbhouse b71
            c"(Phew‚Ä¶ So it‚Äôs just as friends. That's way less pressure knowing that it‚Äôs not a date.)"
            c"(But does that mean the kiss that we shared the other night didn't mean anything, or has he forgotten about it already?)"
            c"(Either way, its kind of nice knowing that [y_name] has asked me to spend time with him and not [s_name].)"
            show sc w3mowbhouse b70
            c"(He must be pretty lonely being so far from home and not having his friends to hang out with.)"
            show sc w3mowbhouse b67
            $ c_points = change_stat(c_points,2,c_name)
            c"Sure, I‚Äôd love to." # +2 COUSIN POINTS"
            if v_w2eow_c_shopping:
                #‚ÄúAdd these lines if the player got all three questions right in ‚ÄúWeek 2 (EOW) Scene 16.5 - The MC visits Cousin in reception‚Äù"
                show sc w3mowbhouse b66
                mc"Awesome!"
                show sc w3mowbhouse b64
                mc"Perhaps we could go to that surf store that you mentioned that you wanted to go to?"
                show sc w3mowbhouse b67
                c"Oh right, of course. Yeah, that‚Äôd be great!"
                show sc w3mowbhouse b71
                c"(I completely forgot that I asked [y_name] if he wanted to do something with me.)"
                c"(I‚Äôm so glad that he still wants to.)"
                #‚ÄúAdd these lines if the player DID NOT get all three questions right in ‚ÄúWeek 2 (EOW) Scene 16.5 - The MC visits Cousin in reception‚Äù"
            else:
                show sc w3mowbhouse b66
                mc"Awesome!"
                show sc w3mowbhouse b64
                mc"I was thinking that we could go to the mall or something like that?"
                show sc w3mowbhouse b66
                c"Actually, I‚Äôve been meaning to check out the new surf store that they have there."
                show sc w3mowbhouse b71
                c"I was thinking of asking if you wanted to come me before, because I figured it might be a place you‚Äôd be interested in seeing."
                show sc w3mowbhouse b66
                mc"Yeah, most definitely!"
                #(scene continues)"

            show sc w3mowbhouse b66
            mc"We can discuss it more later this week."
            show sc w3mowbhouse b64
            mc"So uh, maybe we should head back to the house. I think that should be enough time."
            show sc w3mowbhouse b66
            c"Uh, yeah, it should be."
            mc"Hopefully all is well and by the time we‚Äôve spoken with [s_name], we‚Äôll have a party to start preparing for."
            show sc w3mowbhouse b67
            c"Yeah, let‚Äôs hope so!"
            stop ambient fadeout 1.0
            # (screen goes blank)"
    scene black
    with dissolve
    scene black
    with Pause (2)

    if v_w3mow_night_beach_house_connie:
        jump lb_w3mow_night_beach_house_ending

    $ v_w3mow_night_beach_house_connie = True
    jump lb_w3mow_night_beach_house_connie




label lb_w3mow_night_beach_house_ending:
    # *AFTER BOTH SCENES HAVE PLAYED OUT"
    scene sc w3mowbhouse b72
    with dissolve
    s"Hey [y_name]."
    mc"Hey [s_name]. So‚Ä¶ Are we all good now?"
    mc"I don‚Äôt need to call for any backup or anything like that?"
    show sc w3mowbhouse b73
    s"Haha, I‚Äôm happy to say that we are more than good [y_name]."
    show sc w3mowbhouse b76
    s"Connie and I discussed a few things and I have some very big news to share with you both."
    show sc w3mowbhouse b74
    s"Her eighteenth birthday party WILL be hosted at the hotel this Saturday!"
    mc"That‚Äôs awesome news [s_name]!"
    show sc w3mowbhouse b79
    c"YAY! That‚Äôs wonderful."
    show sc w3mowbhouse b77
    con"Thanks again you guys for making this happen. I‚Äôm so happy right now."
    show sc w3mowbhouse b75
    s"It‚Äôs our pleasure."
    show sc w3mowbhouse b76
    s"We have a lot of work to do, but for today, let‚Äôs just relax and enjoy the afternoon sunshine."
    show sc w3mowbhouse b77
    con"That‚Äôs a great idea."
    show sc w3mowbhouse b73
    s"I mean you're already here, so we may as well make the most of this incredible beach house."
    s"Don‚Äôt you think [y_name]?"
    mc"Yeah, most definitely."
    show sc w3mowbhouse b76
    s"Please help yourselves to anything in the fridge or pantry. There‚Äôs plenty in there."
    show sc w3mowbhouse b72
    s"By the way, you didn‚Äôt happen to bring my phone with you, did you [y_name]?"
    mc"Oh, right! Yes, I did. It‚Äôs in my pocket."
    show sc w3mowbhouse b78
    mc"Here you go."
    # (MC hands the phone to S)"
    s"Thanks."
    show sc w3mowbhouse b74
    s"Oh! That reminds me‚Ä¶"
    # (S stands up)"
    show sc w3mowbhouse b73
    s"Give me a moment guys, I have something to show you all. It‚Äôs a surprise!"
    s"I‚Äôll be right back."
    # (S leaves the room)"
    show sc w3mowbhouse b80
    mc"(Hmm‚Ä¶ I wonder what she has to show us?)"
    scene black
    with dissolve
    scene black
    with Pause (2)











label lb_w3mow_s_uniforms:
    # Week 3 (MOW) 29 - S bought some uniforms for the hotel"
    if _in_replay:
        if y_name == None:
            $ y_name = "MC"
        else:
            $ y_name = persistent.y_name

        if s_name == None:
            $ s_name = "S"
        else:
            $ s_name = persistent.s_name

        if c_name == None:
            $ c_name = "Shortcake"
        else:
            $ c_name = persistent.c_name

        show screen toprightmenu
        play music "music/01/2936-fliegen-by-sascha-ende.mp3"
    scene sc w3mowuniform u05
    with dissolve
    c"What do you think [s_name]‚Äôs big surprise is?"
    mc"I honestly have no idea. Your guess is probably as good as mine [c_name]."
    show sc w3mowuniform u03
    con"Maybe it‚Äôs something to do with the hotel? And perhaps she‚Äôs been planning this over the past few days?"
    mc"Hmm, that‚Äôs a possibility."
    # (S calls out from the other room)"
    show sc w3mowuniform u07
    s"ARE YOU ALL READY FOR THIS?"
    show sc w3mowuniform u06
    c"YEP! READY WHEN YOU ARE [s_name!u]!"
    # (S comes out wearing the new hotel uniforms)"
    show sc w3mowuniform u09
    s"Ta-da!"
    # ROLLING WIP OF S IN THE HOTEL UNIFORM"
    show sc w3mowuniform u14
    mc"Woah‚Ä¶"
    show sc w3mowuniform u08
    c"Oh wow!"
    show sc w3mowuniform u01
    con"What are you wearing [s_name]?"
    show sc w3mowuniform u13
    s"It‚Äôs the new uniform that I designed for the Sunshine Bay lighthouse hotel!"
    s"I had them made up by a local designer that I know in town."
    show sc w3mowuniform u09
    s"She dropped them off here this morning."
    # (S changes pose)"
    show sc w3mowuniform u10
    if persistent.v_xray_enabled:
        show screen scr_peeping_tom("sc w3mowuniform u10","sc w3mowuniform u10x","v_pt_image_index_w3_19")
    s"So, what do we all think?"
    # [It‚Äôs nice / It‚Äôs wonderful / Pretty good]"
    menu:
        "It‚Äôs nice":
            hide screen scr_peeping_tom
            show sc w3mowuniform u11
            mc"It‚Äôs nice [s_name]."
            show sc w3mowuniform u12
            $ s_points = change_stat(s_points,-1,s_name)
            s"(Nice? Is that all he has to say about it?)" #-1 S POINT"
        "It‚Äôs wonderful"(wt="Best choice"):
            hide screen scr_peeping_tom
            show sc w3mowuniform u11
            mc"I think it looks wonderful on you [s_name]."
            show sc w3mowuniform u10
            mc"Your design looks very professional, and I‚Äôm sure that the guests at the hotel will certainly notice."
            show sc w3mowuniform u13
            $ s_points = change_stat(s_points,2,s_name)
            s"(Awesome! I‚Äôm so happy he likes it.)" #+2 S POINTS"
        "Pretty good":
            hide screen scr_peeping_tom
            show sc w3mowuniform u11
            mc"It‚Äôs pretty good."
            mc"I like the old design better, but there‚Äôs nothing wrong with change every so often."
            show sc w3mowuniform u12
            s"(Hmm‚Ä¶ Is that [y_name] saying he doesn‚Äôt like this design?)"
            $ s_points = change_stat(s_points,-1,s_name)
            s"(It‚Äôs kind of hard to tell.)" # -1 S POINT"
    # (scene continues)"
    show sc w3mowuniform u02
    con"I think it looks lovely on you [s_name]."
    show sc w3mowuniform u06
    c"Yeah, you look gorgeous in it."
    show sc w3mowuniform u15
    s"I‚Äôm glad you think so girls because I‚Äôm going to need you both for something."
    show sc w3mowuniform u17
    c"What do you need [s_name]?"
    show sc w3mowuniform u16
    s"I‚Äôve had a few different sizes made up for this uniform, and I was hoping that the two of you would try them on for me."
    show sc w3mowuniform u01
    con"I‚Äôd definitely be up for that!"
    show sc w3mowuniform u04
    con"What about you [c_name]?"
    show sc w3mowuniform u19
    c"Uh, sure. I mean, I guess I‚Äôll have to try it on sooner or later."
    show sc w3mowuniform u16
    s"Great! How about you two use the main bedrooms to get changed."
    show sc w3mowuniform u15
    s"You‚Äôll find some extra uniforms in the ensuite."
    s"There should be the right sizes available for you both."
    show sc w3mowuniform u04
    con"Come on [c_name]. Let‚Äôs go and try them on!"
    show sc w3mowuniform u20
    c"Okay!"
    scene black
    with dissolve
    scene black
    with Pause (2)
    # (cousin and Connie leave the room)"
    scene sc w3mowuniform u22
    with dissolve
    s"So [y_name], tell me, honestly, do you think it was a good idea to get new uniforms for the hotel staff?"
    mc"Probably, yeah."
    mc"I guess I‚Äôll know for sure when we see [c_name] and Connie wearing them."
    mc"I think Ivy and Lily are going to be impressed either way."
    mc"So‚Ä¶ You‚Äôve been using some of your time alone to get these uniforms designed, huh?"
    show sc w3mowuniform u24
    s"I have."
    s"Even though I wasn‚Äôt at the hotel, it didn‚Äôt stop me from doing at least one of the tasks that Ivy and Lily had suggested to me during the wedding after party."
    s"And as I said to you earlier, I was going to come back to the hotel tonight to show you the uniforms..."
    s"But being able to show them to you now is even better!"
    show sc w3mowuniform u25
    s"Speaking of the twins, I should send them a selfie pic of me wearing this."
    show sc w3mowuniform u26
    s"Let me just set my phone up here."
    if v_w3sow_s_selfie_photo:
        # ‚ÄúIF the player chose ONE MORE PHOTO in Scene 03 (Week 3), then her phone screen will show the last photo the MC checked - a topless pic of herself.‚Äù"
        show sc w3mowuniform u27
        s"Okay, let me just-"
        # (screen shakes)"
        show sc w3mowuniform u28
        s"(What the hell??)"
        # (S unlocks her phone and sees the topless pic of herself)"
        s"(Why is this picture of me on my screen? I don‚Äôt remember leaving it like-)"
        # (S looks at the MC)"
        mc"[s_name]? Is everything okay?"
        show sc w3mowuniform u29
        s"(Oh‚Ä¶ I know what‚Äôs happened here. I‚Äôm pretty sure that [y_name] has been through my phone while I was away.)"
        s"(And it looks like he forgot to close my photos app before locking my phone.)"
        s"Yeah, I‚Äôm fine [y_name], but‚Ä¶"
        show sc w3mowuniform u30
        s"Did you go through my phone at all?"
        scene sc w3mowuniform u22
        # [Tell the truth / Lie]"
        menu:
            "Tell the truth"(wt="Best choice"):
                show sc w3mowuniform u22
                mc"Uh, yeah I think I did."
                show sc w3mowuniform u30
                show screen scr_rewards("sc w3mowuniform u30b","v_rewards_s_33")
                s"What for?"
                hide screen scr_rewards
                show sc w3mowuniform u23
                mc"You know, for clues."
                s"Clues? Clues to what?"
                mc"To try and find you of course!"
                show sc w3mowuniform u22
                mc"I thought there might be something in your messages or phone call log that would give me an idea of where you might be."
                show sc w3mowuniform u30
                s"Oh‚Ä¶"
                s"And is that all you checked?"
                show sc w3mowuniform u23
                mc"(Why is she asking me this?)"
                mc"(Oh shit‚Ä¶ I think she knows that I looked through her photos, and the one where she‚Äôs topless.)"
                mc"(Sigh‚Ä¶ I better be honest with her, even if I embarrass myself.)"
                show sc w3mowuniform u22
                mc"No‚Ä¶ I also looked at your photos."
                s"And?"
                mc"I saw something that maybe I shouldn‚Äôt have. I‚Äôm really sorry [s_name]."
                show sc w3mowuniform u31
                s"(Hmm‚Ä¶ Maybe it was an accident.)"
                show sc w3mowuniform u32
                s"(But I‚Äôm happy he at least told me the truth when I asked him for it.)"
                show sc w3mowuniform u25
                $ s_points = change_stat(s_points,2,s_name)
                s"It‚Äôs cool. In future though, you might want to close a person‚Äôs photos app before locking their phone." #+2 S POINTS"
                mc"Ahh shit, so that‚Äôs what I forgot to do."
                show sc w3mowuniform u24
                s"Haha! You almost got away with it [y_name]."
                # (S smiles)"
                show sc w3mowuniform u31
                s"(I wonder what he thought when he saw this picture of me without anything covering my chest?)"
                show sc w3mowuniform u32
                s"(I‚Äôm interested to know, but I might ask him some other time‚Ä¶)"
            "Lie":
                show sc w3mowuniform u23
                mc"(Why would she ask me that? Does [s_name] know that I went through her phone?)"
                mc"(I better play dumb here and hopes that she buys what I‚Äôm about to tell her.)"
                mc"Uh, no, no I didn‚Äôt. Why?"
                show sc w3mowuniform u30
                s"(Hmm‚Ä¶ He straight out lied to me!)"
                s"(If we didn‚Äôt have so much to do, then I‚Äôd call him out on that lie.)"
                show sc w3mowuniform u22
                $ s_points = change_stat(s_points,-2,s_name)
                s"Never mind. It‚Äôs nothing [y_name]. Forget I said anything‚Ä¶" #-2 S POINTS"
                mc"(Phew! Looks like she bought it.)"
                # (scene continues)"
    elif v_w3sow_s_phone:
        # ‚ÄúIF the player chose ‚ÄúGo look for [s_name]‚Äù in Scene 03 (Week 3), then her phone screen will NOT show the topless pic‚Äù"
        show sc w3mowuniform u22
        s"[y_name]... Did you go through my phone at all?"
        mc"Uh, yeah, I think I did."
        s"What for?"
        mc"You know, for clues."
        show sc w3mowuniform u30
        s"Clues? Clues to what?"
        show sc w3mowuniform u22
        mc"To try and find you of course!"
        mc"I thought there might be something in your messages or phone call log that would give me an idea of where you might be."
        show sc w3mowuniform u23
        s"Oh, okay‚Ä¶"
        show sc w3mowuniform u30
        show screen scr_rewards("sc w3mowuniform u29b","v_rewards_s_33")
        s"(I guess that makes sense.)"
        hide screen scr_rewards
    scene black
    with dissolve
    scene black
    with Pause (2)
    # (the girls return to model the new uniforms - you could consider making cousin and Connie‚Äôs both different to S‚Äô design, bit with the same colours, logos)"
    # (Connie calls out from the other room)"
    scene sc w3mowuniform u07
    with dissolve
    con"WE‚ÄôRE READY YOU TWO!"
    s"ALL RIGHT, COME ON OUT!"
    # (Connie and Cousin walk into the living room wearing the new hotel uniforms)"
    # ROLLING WIP OF THE GIRLS IN THE HOTEL UNIFORM"
    show sc w3mowuniform u33
    s"Here they come."
    show sc w3mowuniform u35
    mc"(Good lord...)"
    show sc w3mowuniform u36
    if persistent.v_xray_enabled:
        show screen scr_peeping_tom("sc w3mowuniform u36","sc w3mowuniform u36x","v_pt_image_index_w3_20")
    s"What do you think of the girls in these designs [y_name]?"
    s"They look great, right?"
    hide screen scr_peeping_tom
    show sc w3mowuniform u35
    mc"They look fantastic‚Ä¶ You did very well with creating these ensembles [s_name]."
    s"How do they feel ladies?"
    show sc w3mowuniform u35
    con"They feel incredible against my skin. It‚Äôs a perfect fit."
    show sc w3mowuniform u36
    con"Do you think I look like someone who could work at the hotel [y_name]?"
    # (Connie changes her pose)"
    mc"Yeah, for sure."
    show sc w3mowuniform u33
    s"And you [c_name]?"
    # (the uniform look a little short around the hem of cousin‚Äôs outfit)"
    show sc w3mowuniform u37
    c"Hmm, I don‚Äôt know..."
    show sc w3mowuniform u38
    c"Do you think that it‚Äôs maybe a little too short?"
    # (Cousin turns around and we see how short it looks from the back)"
    s"It looks perfectly fine to me."
    show sc w3mowuniform u22
    s"What do you think [y_name]?"
    # [I agree / She‚Äôs right]"
    menu:
        "I agree":
            show sc w3mowuniform u38
            mc"I have to agree with [s_name], I think it looks great on you [c_name]."
            mc"And there‚Äôs nothing wrong with wearing a dress that‚Äôs a little shorter, not that this one is."
            $ c_points = change_stat(c_points,-2,c_name)
            c"Hmm‚Ä¶ If you say so." #-2 COUSIN POINTS"
            c"Do you think I could wear something a little more conservative instead [s_name]?"
            show sc w3mowuniform u33
            s"Uh, sure you can [c_name]. I'll figure something out."
            show sc w3mowuniform u38
            c"Thanks."
            # (Cousin gives an unsure look here)"
        "She‚Äôs right"(wt="Best choice"):
            show sc w3mowuniform u38
            mc"Actually, I think [c_name] could be right [s_name]. It does seem a little short."
            mc"And if staff members are going to be walking around the hotel..."
            show sc w3mowuniform u22
            mc"Then we don‚Äôt want to give the guests something to complain about."
            mc"Especially the older ones. We want to look professional and even little things like this need to be closely assessed."
            show sc w3mowuniform u23
            s"Hmm‚Ä¶ Maybe you‚Äôre right."
            show sc w3mowuniform u33
            s"Okay, I‚Äôll get my designer to adjust the hem so it‚Äôs a little lower."
            mc"Good call."
            show sc w3mowuniform u38
            c"(Wow, I‚Äôm so glad [y_name] said something to [s_name]...)"
            $ c_points = change_stat(c_points,2,c_name)
            c"(As I don‚Äôt think I could‚Äôve worn this behind the reception desk without feeling a little paranoid about the short length.)" # +2 COUSIN POINTS"
            c"(I‚Äôm certain that anyone could see my panties if I bent over in this dress!)"
    # (scene continues)"
    show sc w3mowuniform u25
    s"There‚Äôs just one more question that needs to be asked and answered. And it‚Äôs the most important one of the lot."
    # (S turns to the MC)"
    show sc w3mowuniform u39
    if persistent.v_xray_enabled:
        show screen scr_peeping_tom("sc w3mowuniform u39","sc w3mowuniform u39x","v_pt_image_index_w3_21")
    s"[y_name]? Who do you think looks the best in these designs?"
    mc"Huh? You seriously want me to answer that?"
    hide screen scr_peeping_tom
    show sc w3mowuniform u40
    s"Of course!"
    show sc w3mowuniform u41
    s"We need a male‚Äôs expert opinion and you‚Äôre the only guy here."
    show sc w3mowuniform u42
    con"Come on [y_name], just be honest with us."
    con"I‚Äôm sure the two girls you don‚Äôt pick won‚Äôt be offended."
    con"(I wonder if [y_name] is going to choose me?)"
    show sc w3mowuniform u43
    c"(I don‚Äôt know why, but I really hope he picks me.)"
    show sc w3mowuniform u41
    s"(I‚Äôm pretty sure that [y_name] will tell the other two that I look the best.)"
    s"(Not that it‚Äôs a contest to win anything special..)"
    s"(Still, it would be nice to be told that this outfit looks better on me than [c_name] and Connie.)"
    s"(But it‚Äôs his choice.)"
    show sc w3mowuniform u39
    s"So what‚Äôs your decision [y_name]?"
    # (the three girls look at him, posing)"
    mc"(Ah shit‚Ä¶ They‚Äôre all staring at me.)"
    mc"(No matter who I choose, two girls aren‚Äôt going to be happy, regardless of what Connie just said.)"
    mc"(I mean they all look sensational, so there really isn‚Äôt a wrong answer here.)"
    mc"(But most girls don‚Äôt think like that.)"
    mc"(Sigh‚Ä¶)"
    show sc w3mowuniform u41
    mc"All right, but before I answer..."
    show sc w3mowuniform u42
    mc"I just want you to know that I think that all three of you look incredible in these new hotel designs..."
    show sc w3mowuniform u43
    mc"And I‚Äôm looking forward to seeing the staff at the hotel wearing them in the future."
    show sc w3mowuniform u39
    mc"But my favourite would have to be‚Ä¶"
    # [ [s_name] / [c_name] / Connie]"
    menu:
        "[s_name]"(wt="Favour [s_name]"):
            mc"‚Ä¶ [s_name]."
            show sc w3mowuniform u40
            s"(YES!!)"
            s"Any reason why [y_name]?"
            $ s_points = change_stat(s_points,2,s_name)
            mc"I just think the design suits you the best [s_name]. And that‚Äôs all I have to say about that." #+2 S POINTS"
        "[c_name]"(wt="Favour [c_name]"):
            mc"‚Ä¶ [c_name]."
            show sc w3mowuniform u43
            c"(Oh my! He chose ME!)"
            c"Any reason why [y_name]?"
            $ c_points = change_stat(c_points,2,c_name)
            mc"I just think the design suits [c_name] the best. And that‚Äôs all I have to say about that." #+2 COUSIN POINTS"
        "Connie"(wt="Favour Connie"):
            mc"‚Ä¶ Connie."
            show sc w3mowuniform u42
            con"(Oh wow! I‚Äôm genuinely surprised that he chose me instead of [s_name] and [c_name].)"
            con"Any reason why [y_name]?"
            $ connie_points = change_stat(connie_points,2,"Connie")
            mc"I just think the design suits Connie the best. And that‚Äôs all I have to say about that." #+2 CONNIE POINTS"
            # (scene continues)"
    show sc w3mowuniform u39
    s"Fair enough."
    con"Thanks for letting us know [y_name]."
    show sc w3mowuniform u42
    con"I‚Äôm sure that couldn‚Äôt have been easy for you."
    mc"Ha! You have no idea!"
    play sound "sound effects/01/02/female_laughing_giggling.mp3"
    show sc w3mowuniform u40
    s"Hahaha!"
    show sc w3mowuniform u39
    s"Okay, why don‚Äôt the three of us get changed, and then maybe we could get going to give Connie some time to herself?"
    show sc w3mowuniform u44
    con"Actually, why don‚Äôt you all stay for dinner?"
    show sc w3mowuniform u47
    s"Really? You want us to stay?"
    show sc w3mowuniform u45
    con"Yeah, I‚Äôd love it if you could."
    con"That is if it‚Äôs all right with the three of you. We can order some takeout!"
    show sc w3mowuniform u46
    s"Okay, I like that idea."
    show sc w3mowuniform u48
    s"How about you two?"
    show sc w3mowuniform u49
    c"I guess I could stay a little while longer. But I definitely have to make sure that I return home tonight."
    c"My Mom will probably be home tonight so I better make sure that I am too."
    show sc w3mowuniform u50
    s"We‚Äôll get you home safely."
    show sc w3mowuniform u42
    con"And what about you [y_name]?"
    con"Are you up for having dinner with three pretty young ladies?"
    mc"(Damn‚Ä¶ Now there‚Äôs a question that I don‚Äôt get asked every day!)"
    mc"(Sigh‚Ä¶)"
    mc"How could I say no to that? Yeah, count me in!"
    show sc w3mowuniform u39
    s"All right, wait right here [y_name] and the three of us will be back before you know it!"
    if _in_replay:
        scene black
        with dissolve
        scene black
        with Pause (2)
    $ persistent.replay_w3_mow_s_uniforms = False
    $ renpy.end_replay()
    scene black
    with dissolve
    scene black
    with Pause (2)
















label lb_w3mow_mc_girls_dinner:
    #     Week 3 (MOW) 30 - MC, S, and SC have dinner together and celebrate Father's day"
    scene sc w3mowdinner d34
    with dissolve
    play ambient "sound effects/01/00/soft_ocean_waves.mp3" fadein 1.0
    con"How‚Äôs dinner everyone?"
    show sc w3mowdinner d12
    s"This is amazing Connie! Do you normally get food delivered?"
    show sc w3mowdinner d33
    show screen scr_rewards("sc w3mowdinner d33b","v_rewards_connie_5")
    con"Not always, no."
    con"But my parents have connections to the restaurant owners and I‚Äôd sometimes have lunch there on weekends."
    hide screen scr_rewards
    show sc w3mowdinner d15
    c"Do you think you and your family will do anything for Father‚Äôs Day this weekend?"
    show sc w3mowdinner d37
    con"Oh, I think it‚Äôs highly unlikely, especially after my Dad finds out that my plans have changed for my party."
    show sc w3mowdinner d14
    c"Oh, right. of course."
    show sc w3mowdinner d31
    con"What about you three? Will you all be spending it with family or your father‚Äôs?"
    # (Connie takes a drink of her wine)"
    show sc w3mowdinner d39
    s"Oh, there‚Äôs pretty much no chance of that happening Connie."
    show sc w3mowdinner d32
    con"You‚Äôre not close with your Dad either?"
    show sc w3mowdinner d11
    s"Well‚Ä¶"
    jump lb_w3mow_mc_girls_dinner_1

label lb_w3mow_mc_girls_dinner_1:
    show sc w3mowdinner d11
    s"I‚Äôve never met my father."
    show sc w3mowdinner d32
    con"Oh, I‚Äôm so sorry [s_name], I had no idea."
    show sc w3mowdinner d09
    s"It‚Äôs cool."
    show sc w3mowdinner d08
    s"The closest person I‚Äôve ever had to a father-figure was when [y_name]‚Äôs Dad, Gerald, dated my mother for about five or so years..."
    show sc w3mowdinner d09
    s"And we all lived together under the same roof."
    show sc w3mowdinner d29
